pnp:CanvasControlProperty.Value: WELCOME TO CONTOSO ELECTRONICS

❝

It’s my pleasure to extend a warm welcome to each one of you as you get ready to join Contoso Electronics. This is an environment where our employees can make an impact and make a difference. Use this opportunity to pursue whatever drives your passion. I personally feel the big reason for continuing to grow as a company and continuing to attract new talent is because we need you to help us figure out what the new world is all about.

Get ready for your first day

We know starting a new job is exciting but can be stressful. Our priority is to make you feel welcome and to set you up for success. Use this checklist to prepare for your first day.
BE PREPARED

• Complete all of your employment forms
  • Learn more about Contoso
  • Reach out to your HR contacts with any questions
WHAT TO BRING

• Two forms of official identification
  • Mobile phone
  • Comfortable walking shoes (we will give you a tour of the office)
WHAT TO EXPECT

• Your manager will greet you in the lobby of building 92 at 9:00am
  • A company issued laptop will become available for use on your first day
  • Introduction and meeting scheduled with your onboarding buddy
  • Lunch with your team in your first week
  • Participation in a one-day orientation
NEW-HIRE ORIENTATION

• Official welcome into Contoso community and culture
  • Learn about Contoso mission and values
  • Introduction to your benefits and company perks
  • Tips from recent new-hires 
  • Receive and set up computer with the help of IT
  • Learn about next-steps in your onboarding journey
  • Time for questions and answers
WHERE TO GO

pnp:CanvasControlProperty.Value:
OUR VALUES

Guiding Principles

Our collective experiences make up Contoso. Our products, services, communications, and people all contribute to the perception of our brand. Together we're defining what it means to be Contoso. We aspire to be a brand that is authentic, inspiring, and relevant. We want to earn people's love, creating fans that will advocate on our behalf. And you play an important part in doing that. We create fans by staying approachable, practicing empathy, and being determined.

pnp:CanvasControlProperty.Value:
BELONGING FOR EVERYONE

Diversity and inclusion

Our first priority is to establish a sense of belonging for everyone. We invest in diversity and inclusion because in order for each individual to bring their best self to work, a sense of belonging must be established. Empathetic leadership is key. Diversity and inclusion is a value and initiative that is owned by the entire leadership team.

pnp:CanvasControlProperty.Value:
GIVING BACK

Investing in community

Investing in our communities is a great way to give back to those that have helped support our business from the early days. We invest in our communities by coordinating volunteer groups for nonprofit work and pro-bono projects on a quarterly basis. Over the years we have committed ourselves to regular financial investments in after-school programs that teach kids about STEM and robotics. We continue to look for more opportunities to invest in our community.

COLLABORATION & CREATIVITY

Teamwork

Some say "team work makes the dream work" - and we agree. In order to solve complex problems, teams are more effective than individuals. Teamwork allows for collaboration and sparks creativity, which results in producing better products for our customers.

pnp:CanvasControlProperty.Value:
A MESSAGE FROM OUR CVP

The world changes when we change our perspective.

It’s my pleasure to extend a warm welcome to each one of you as you get ready to join Contoso Electronics. This is an environment where our employees can make an impact and make a difference. Use this opportunity to pursue whatever drives your passion. I personally feel the big reason for continuing to grow as a company and continuing to attract new talent is because we need you to help us figure out what the new world is all about.

pnp:CanvasControlProperty.Value:
OUR HUMBLE BEGINNINGS

How it all started​​​​​​​

Contoso was created in the garages of creators and engineers in 2008. Ten years later, we celebrated a million drones sold. Contoso is built upon innovation and cutting edge technology. From the beginning, we were willing to take risks and make big bets on what we thought our customers would need in the future. Today, we are committed more than ever to providing  solutions that help our customers see the world form a new perspective.

pnp:CanvasControlProperty.Value:
AUTHENTIC, INSPIRING, RELEVANT

Our brand

Our collective experiences make up Contoso. Our products, services, communications, and people all contribute to the perception of our brand. Together we're defining what it means to be Contoso. We aspire to be a brand that is authentic, inspiring, and relevant. We want to earn people's love, creating fans that will advocate on our behalf. And you play an important part in doing that. We create fans by staying approachable, practicing empathy, and being determined.

Staying approachable

We don't want customers to be intimidated by technology.

Practicing empathy

We listen to people, seeking to understand their goals, hopes, and concerns.

Being determined

We're committed to advancing the many ways people achieve today, inspiring action, and anticipating what they'll need tomorrow.

Prioritizing creativity

Our platform starts with the vision of talented creators. We give these creators the tools they need to bring their ideas to life.

pnp:CanvasControlProperty.Value:
A MESSAGE FROM CONTOSO'S PRESIDENT

The world changes when we change our perspective.

It’s my pleasure to extend a warm welcome to each one of you as you join Contoso Electronics. This is an environment where our employees can make an impact and make a difference. Use this opportunity to pursue whatever drives your passion. I personally feel the big reason for continuing to grow as a company and continuing to attract new talent is because we need you to help us figure out what the new world is all about.

pnp:CanvasControlProperty.Value:
CONTOSO ELECTRONICS​​​​​​​

At Contoso we never forget that teams are first made up of individuals who have different perspectives that are necessary to drive innovation and industry growth. Every team at Contoso contributes the over all customer-impact we are able to make as an organization. We consider our success a reflection of the investments we make in our people. Explore the team pages for each department to learn more about how the business works, what each team is responsible for and how your new role fits in with the company mission and vision.

pnp:CanvasControlProperty.Value:
Customer Service

The customer service department is responsible for client assistance on the phone, via chat, and on-site.  Customer service representatives often act as the face as the company because they are interacting with customers most of the time. Our customer service team is a highly valued role at Contoso because we know the value of current customer support is a good investment for the long-term growth of the entire company.

Engineering

Contoso engineers come in many forms and work towards goals of building, troubleshooting, and maintaining complex systems for both software and hardware products. Engineers work side-by-side with product and design teams to develop cutting edge technology that's often the first of its kind.

pnp:CanvasControlProperty.Value:
Marketing

The marketing department is responsible for understanding and responding to market demands as well and the company brand and identity. The marketing team is also responsible for working alongside creative agencies and industry partners to develop advertising opportunities across various media types. The marketing team works closely with the sales team and customer service to understand our customers ever changing needs.

Hello everyone! 👋🏼​​​​​​​

I'm Adele Vance. I'm from Yucatan, Mexico and I'm joining Engineering team. I’m thrilled to be joining Contoso Electronics. I’ve long been a fan and an early adopter of the latest technologies, and nothing could be better than joining a company that is on the cutting edge of innovation in this area. I see so much great talent here, and my focus will be on harnessing the experience, ideas, and skills of everyone in the organization to advance Contoso Electronics as THE industry leader. When I’m not at work, I enjoy hiking with my dog, boating, and volunteering.


Look forward to meeting you!

Use this checklist as your guide for the next 90 days. Work alongside your manager to prioritize tasks and get introductions to colleagues you will be collaborating with. Remember, sometimes growth can be uncomfortable so take it one day at a time and never hesitate to reach out for support.

pnp:CanvasControlProperty.Value:
INTRODUCTIONS TO THE TEAM​​​​​​​

Write an intro

We want to get to know you. Make your arrival known in an "About me" introductory news post that will be shared with the engineering organization.

Introduce yourself to the team, share fun facts, and even include pictures of your family or pets! Once published, your post will show up in Contoso engineering news.

pnp:CanvasControlProperty.Value:
A MESSAGE FROM OUR CVP

The world changes when we change our perspective.

It’s my pleasure to extend a warm welcome to each one of you as you get ready to join Contoso Electronics. This is an environment where our employees can make an impact and make a difference. Use this opportunity to pursue whatever drives your passion. I personally feel the big reason for continuing to grow as a company and continuing to attract new talent is because we need you to help us figure out what the new world is all about.

Connect with us on Yammer or Microsoft Teams. ​​​​​​​

pnp:CanvasControlProperty.Value:
FY20: BALANCED INNOVATION

Our priorities are a reflection of our values, perspectives, big-bets in technology, and the needs of our customers.

In 2020, we are focusing on high-impact investments that balance innovations in the areas of engineering, product development, and customer engagement.

Modernize core experiences​​​​​​​

Improve product usability and accuracy for core modern workloads to increase product adoption for low-confident user segment by 20%.

pnp:CanvasControlProperty.Value:
Grow usage across business segments

Develop a new self-help online resource center that offers video tutorials, and a new quick answers content experience to increase customer confidence and reduce support calls by 15%.

pnp:CanvasControlProperty.Value:
Focus on end users and drive engagement

Invest in R&D to develop a communication model that will double current user engagement and attract new consumer retail accounts.

pnp:CanvasControlProperty.Value:
Hello everyone! 👋🏼​​​​​​​

I'm Adele Vance. I'm from Yucatan, Mexico and I'm joining Engineering team. I’m thrilled to be joining Contoso Electronics. I’ve long been a fan and an early adopter of the latest technologies, and nothing could be better than joining a company that is on the cutting edge of innovation in this area. I see so much great talent here, and my focus will be on harnessing the experience, ideas, and skills of everyone in the organization to advance Contoso Electronics as THE industry leader. When I’m not at work, I enjoy hiking with my dog, boating, and volunteering.


Looking forward to meeting you!

HELLO 👋

Welcome to Contoso Sales, we're excited to have you on the team.

We are dedicated to sales excellence because its responsible for our business growth and connection with customers. We want to help you reach your career goals by continuously investing in your growth and development. We can't wait to get to know you, and to see you grow with us!​​​​​​​

GETTING STARTED

Onboarding checklist

Use this checklist as your guide for the next 90 days. Work alongside your manager to prioritize tasks and get introductions to colleagues you will be collaborating with. Remember, sometimes growth can be uncomfortable so take it one day at a time and never hesitate to reach out for support.

pnp:CanvasControlProperty.Value:
INTRODUCTIONS TO THE TEAM​​​​​​​

Write an intro

We want to get to know you. Make your arrival known in an "About me" introductory news post that will be shared with the sales organization.

Introduce yourself to the team, share fun facts, and even include pictures of your family or pets! Once published, your post will show up in Contoso sales news.

pnp:CanvasControlProperty.Value:
A MESSAGE FROM OUR CVP

The world changes when we change our perspective

It’s my pleasure to extend a warm welcome to each one of you as you get ready to join Contoso Electronics. This is an environment where our employees can make an impact and make a difference. Use this opportunity to pursue whatever drives your passion. I personally feel the big reason for continuing to grow as a company and continuing to attract new talent is because we need you to help us figure out what the new world is all about.

Business Development

Business development focuses on pursuing strategic opportunities that align with our products and value proposition. The role of business development is to cultivate partnerships, commercial relationships and identify new market opportunities. Business development works closely with account managers and marketing to keep a pulse on customer feedback and needs.
